<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-05-05T16:40:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-05-05T16:40:00-05:00" n="295" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d295">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/203.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Sullivan</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-05-05T17:00:00-04:40">
                                    <hi rend="italic">May 5, 1914, 5 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The following telegram has been received from Henry, Puerto Plata: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Nautilus</hi> has ordered discontinuance
                                    artillery by both sides. The situation outwardly same but Bordas
                                    probably weakening.</p>
                            </quote>
                        </p>
                        <p>Henry also wires Arias is in Puerto Plata with several hundred soldiers.
                            Reenforcements for Bordas leaving here to-morrow night.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Sullivan</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>